WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.629
Good morning family. How are y'all

00:00:02.639 --> 00:00:04.309
doing today? Praise the Lord.

00:00:04.319 --> 00:00:06.390
Thank you for joining me. I was out

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:09.030
praying today and I was talking

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:10.390
to the Lord, just getting direction for

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.230
this channel and

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:14.310
listening, being quiet, listening about

00:00:14.320 --> 00:00:16.310
the economy and where we

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:18.550
are. He said, 'Brandon, you

00:00:18.560 --> 00:00:20.870
don't realize, but I've assembled some

00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:23.590
of the greatest prayer warriors of this

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:26.390
generation on this channel, and there

00:00:26.390 --> 00:00:26.400
are

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:29.429
a lot of you who are veterans that have

00:00:29.439 --> 00:00:32.870
been praying for decades and

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:35.430
know how to pray.'He said,

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:37.510
'Brandon, I've called you to come on here

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:40.229
and lead them into

00:00:40.239 --> 00:00:42.470
prayer. They know more than you—a lot

00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:43.830
of them know more than

00:00:43.830 --> 00:00:43.840
you—but

00:00:43.840 --> 00:00:45.910
they're here to pray with you. I've

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:48.310
assembled them here to pray with

00:00:48.310 --> 00:00:48.320
you.'It

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:51.110
was like a

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:53.750
slap in the head, just like

00:00:53.750 --> 00:00:53.760
'duh,'you

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:57.430
know? The words that

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:59.590
He's giving me, folks—the words that

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:02.310
He's talking to me about regarding the great

00:01:02.320 --> 00:01:04.390
shaking, the great awakening,

00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:06.630
the economy, and the

00:01:06.630 --> 00:01:06.640
shelves—they are

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:08.670
things

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:11.390
to pray

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:14.310
about.

00:01:14.320 --> 00:01:15.590
I'm getting pieces; I'm getting

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:17.510
corrected, y'all. So, I'm just

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:20.469
letting you all in on my world.

00:01:20.479 --> 00:01:22.469
He said to me, 'I've called you

00:01:22.479 --> 00:01:25.670
to be a prophetic

00:01:25.670 --> 00:01:25.680
intercessor.'He

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:27.510
came to me and said,

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:30.390
'Brandon, look at these trade wars

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:33.270
going on right now. I told

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:36.230
you about these back in 2023 to

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:39.590
warn you.'He said, 'So

00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:41.670
what are you going to do about

00:01:41.670 --> 00:01:41.680
it?'That

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:43.590
was several

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:46.230
days ago, about a week or so ago,

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:48.230
and I said, 'Well, I guess I'll bring

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:50.030
it and start praying over

00:01:50.030 --> 00:01:50.040
it.'The

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:54.109
moment we started to attack

00:01:54.119 --> 00:01:57.429
that in the spirit realm, it started to

00:01:57.439 --> 00:02:00.069
shift and change. The Lord said to

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:02.030
me, 'Look at the fruit of what you're

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:04.310
doing.

00:02:04.320 --> 00:02:06.389
There's fruit in what I've called

00:02:06.399 --> 00:02:10.229
you to do. Look, they're all of a sudden

00:02:10.239 --> 00:02:13.350
in Switzerland

00:02:13.350 --> 00:02:13.360
talking.'All

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:15.510
these weeks have gone by, and

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:16.949
if there's a trade war,

00:02:16.959 --> 00:02:18.070
there's going to be a deficit. There are going

00:02:18.070 --> 00:02:18.080
to be empty

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:19.750
shelves, folks.

00:02:19.760 --> 00:02:21.430
I just

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:22.630
took it as, 'Well, that's going to

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:24.070
happen; it's set in

00:02:24.070 --> 00:02:24.080
stone.'There

00:02:24.080 --> 00:02:25.110
will

00:02:25.120 --> 00:02:26.630
be prescription shortages

00:02:26.640 --> 00:02:27.990
throughout America and you won't be able

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.869
to get your medicine. So, when we

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:32.630
started praying against that, look what

00:02:32.640 --> 00:02:33.830
happened with the prescription

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:35.830
medicines.

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:38.309
Donald Trump

00:02:38.309 --> 00:02:38.319
said

00:02:38.319 --> 00:02:40.869
today, 'Hey, we're going to

00:02:40.879 --> 00:02:43.430
lower the price of prescriptions and

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:46.309
make them inexpensive for

00:02:46.309 --> 00:02:46.319
you—some

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:48.110
of them by

00:02:48.110 --> 00:02:48.120
80%.'We

00:02:48.120 --> 00:02:50.390
started praying into

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:51.910
prescriptions and they suddenly

00:02:51.910 --> 00:02:51.920
started

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:54.470
dropping in price. He starts

00:02:54.480 --> 00:02:56.790
doing stuff with prescription

00:02:56.790 --> 00:02:56.800
medicines—not

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:59.990
a shortage, but God's trying to

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:01.670
bless His people as we started praying

00:03:01.680 --> 00:03:04.390
for them. Then China and America start

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:05.670
saying, 'Hey, we're going to negotiate

00:03:05.680 --> 00:03:08.790
in Switzerland.'All these major things

00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:11.430
start happening as these

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:13.750
great prayer warriors

00:03:13.760 --> 00:03:15.949
assemble

00:03:15.959 --> 00:03:19.509
together praying.

00:03:19.519 --> 00:03:22.869
I'm sorry,

00:03:22.879 --> 00:03:24.630
folks. I don't want to be

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.710
critical of anybody until I

00:03:26.710 --> 00:03:26.720
