00:03:34.239 --> 00:03:36.149
these things and I've said,

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:37.589
'Well, it's to pray about

00:03:37.589 --> 00:03:37.599
it.'No,

00:03:37.599 --> 00:03:39.589
really, seriously,

00:03:39.589 --> 00:03:39.599
Goofy—you're

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:41.110
supposed to really pray about

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:43.750
this stuff.

00:03:43.760 --> 00:03:46.070
After he showed me the

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:48.949
change in that, he said, 'Pray for

00:03:48.959 --> 00:03:51.030
Trump and what's going to happen in the

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:52.470
Middle

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:55.470
East.'There

00:03:55.480 --> 00:03:58.229
are

00:03:58.239 --> 00:03:59.990
major things that will happen with

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:03.229
digital assets. You need to pray over

00:04:03.229 --> 00:04:03.239
these

00:04:03.239 --> 00:04:05.589
things that will not be released

00:04:05.599 --> 00:04:08.070
all at once, but they're working on

00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:10.470
something for a wealth transfer. I told

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:13.589
you Saudi Arabia and the Middle East will

00:04:13.599 --> 00:04:16.390
rise up out of the ashes. They'll become

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:19.990
the superpowers of the earth.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:23.350
What started in the

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:26.310
Middle East with the Garden of Eden will

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:29.590
finish in the Middle East.

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:33.629
Iraq,

00:04:33.639 --> 00:04:36.790
Syria,

00:04:36.800 --> 00:04:39.830
Jordan, Israel,

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:42.950
Turkey, and Egypt will start to

00:04:42.960 --> 00:04:45.030
