00:05:38.919 --> 00:05:41.510
Venezuela. I warned you about Venezuela.

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:44.230
'Oh, poor Venezuela, come up out

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:45.670
of there. We'll

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:47.310
bring you into the

00:05:49.150 --> 00:05:49.160
BRICS.'Cuba,

00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:54.629
Iran, North Korea,

00:05:54.639 --> 00:05:57.670
China, and all these other nations

00:05:57.680 --> 00:06:00.870
