00:06:00.880 --> 00:06:02.710
in, brothers. You've been

00:06:02.710 --> 00:06:02.720
outcasts.

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:05.350
Let's join up together and

00:06:05.360 --> 00:06:08.390
