00:06:08.390 --> 00:06:08.400
and

00:06:08.400 --> 00:06:11.350
global financial

00:06:11.350 --> 00:06:11.360
system.'I

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:14.469
saw these

00:06:14.479 --> 00:06:18.150
