00:06:23.120 --> 00:06:25.430
Some of these people are very evil,

00:06:25.430 --> 00:06:25.440
communist

00:06:25.440 --> 00:06:27.430
men.

00:06:27.430 --> 00:06:27.440
Look

00:06:27.440 --> 00:06:29.270
at

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:31.590
Kim Jong-un; he is a very

00:06:31.600 --> 00:06:34.390
evil man. Look at how he treats his

00:06:34.400 --> 00:06:36.710
people. You see Iran,

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:40.309
Venezuela, and

00:06:40.319 --> 00:06:41.830
Cuba.

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:44.070
These people are outcasts for a

00:06:44.080 --> 00:06:48.070
reason. They're going to Russia

00:06:48.070 --> 00:06:48.080
